               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnna “Book of the Christening” (fols. 1ra-18va,
                     27ra-28vb), incomplete
 II) Excerpt from a lectionary (fols. 19ra-26vb,
                     29ra-35rb, 36ra-rb), unidentified
 III) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”
                     
 III-1) Introductory exhortation (fol. 35va-vb, 37ra-vb), incomplete
                     IV) Excerpt from Maṣḥafa krǝstǝnnā “Book of the Christening” (fols.
                     38va-39vb)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I is called Maṣḥafa ṭǝmqat in the incipit (<locus target="#1r">1r</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
