                        36ra-rb.</handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h4" script="Ethiopic"> Hand c: <locus target="#35va">35va-</locus>vb,
                        37ra-vb.</handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h5" script="Ethiopic"> Hand d: <locus from="38va" to="39rb">38va-39rb</locus>.</handNote>
